      <title>美国航空警告第一季度意外亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-23/american-airlines-warns-of-surprise-first-quarter-loss-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国航空集团公司 (American Airlines Group Inc.) 预计第一季度调整后每股亏损将高达 40 美分，因为它正努力赢回商务旅客并应对高昂的成本。彭博情报的乔治·弗格森 (George Ferguson) 对此进行了更详细的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-23/american-airlines-warns-of-surprise-first-quarter-loss-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 15:30:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克与奥特曼的不和与他对特朗普的忠诚相冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-23/musk-s-feud-with-altman-collides-with-devotion-to-trump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的马克斯·查夫金表示，埃隆·马斯克对萨姆·奥特曼的反复批评触及了有关星际之门人工智能计划的一些合理问题。但查夫金在“彭博公开兴趣”上表示，对于唐纳德·特朗普总统的高级顾问来说，这是一个奇怪的立场。索纳莉·巴萨克的华尔街快讯于周五发布。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-23/musk-s-feud-with-altman-collides-with-devotion-to-trump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 15:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管供应过剩加剧，智利仍对扩大锂资源开发抱有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/chile-keeps-faith-in-lithium-expansion-despite-worsening-glut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利拥有全球最大的锂储量，尽管全球锂资源供应日益紧张，对电池金属行业造成了巨大挤压，但该国相信投资者仍将竞相争夺新矿床的开采许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/chile-keeps-faith-in-lithium-expansion-despite-worsening-glut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 15:20:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
